        <updated>2008-11-22T00:54:15-06:00</updated>
        <summary>The "Good" - understanding that marketing is an investment not an expense, and a science not an art I recommend that you read Sergio Zyman's first book, "The End of Marketing as We Know It." Sergio is infamous as the...</summary>
        <author>
            <name>Todd Ebert</name>
        </author>
        <category scheme="http://www.sixapart.com/ns/types#category" term="Books" />
        
        <category scheme="http://sixapart.com/ns/types#tag" term="business book" />
